lip;」<br />\n<br />\n跟住衝左上天台，叫左一聲「鳴呀，點解係我」就跳左落去，成班同事追上去都追唔切，有兩個女同事嚇到暈左，仲有個男同事當場嚇到變左弱智，不停問人要唔要食腸仔蛋。<br />\n<br />\n我就好好彩無咩事，但同班同事五十幾個人即時變左失業，你條仆街真係害人害物&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"84c81e7e26b6f791889204457d7309535aabf6e8","tid":246624,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T07:37:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日北韓北韓北韓講左幾廿年<br />\n屌<br />\n煩唔煩呀<br />\n打又唔撚會打<br />\n中共同條肥仔金驚9 你咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講左幾廿年<br />\n北韓由冇核子都攪到似乎有喇<br />\n共慘宜家都完全冇野怕咁滯<br />\n繼續吹囉<br />\n煩撚到呢"},{"pid":"85bb7b04fe0d9ce3725e722b3951331d90465dda","tid":246624,"uid":3794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T07:42:44.000Z","msg":"睇到新唐人就知唔使認真理呢單新聞"},{"pid":"3e47c060edf73218515b06e3ad2e6222d09b0149","tid":246624,"uid":101632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T07:47:18.000Z","msg":"驚人協議?雜總送多幾件親戚去美國做人質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f51fb4e096b08490b32400734eea5e988255279d","tid":246624,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T07:55:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇到新唐人就知唔使認真理呢單新聞</blockquote><br />\n當睇故事 猜吓迷"},{"pid":"ed51e080c910b96d1e6d4ba25855ad9964c174f7","tid":246624,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T09:31:46.000Z","msg":"驚人協議有冇肥仔金份? <br />\n你話同肥仔金有驚人協議反而有可信性。<br />\n家陣三日唔埋兩日射飛彈係肥仔金喎。"},{"pid":"a46f2e92e6c0b9be6b963a0fd2db06fd4e81c2fb","tid":246624,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T09:54:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中共都on99<br />\n你諗下中美聯手<br />\n估下北韓最後2選1投靠美定中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家好似埋俄佬堆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中咩美者，世界上同美國對敵，唔一家就要埋中共邊。<br />\n俄羅斯，中東果邊都得。"},{"pid":"b60277d9eac4385511fc28e848d47c52358bcfff","tid":246624,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T10:27:42.000Z","msg":"清咗北韓，再駐美軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dcad4ef1ac4153a6468fc78d711d64a0cf5c81a","tid":246624,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T10:41:21.000Z","msg":"嗯 一個月後北泡自己中Wanna Cry 自己核爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}